description.narrative:
The overall stated objective of PPAN programme is "to contribute towards the development of a democratic and pluralistic society that respects human rights and enhances Palestinian national identity". PPAN's programme has defined three major outcomes that are well linked to a set of verifiable indicators, specific outputs and targets. The three outcomes are:

a) Functionality, recognition and sustainability of an active performing arts network are bolstered;
b) Young women, children and youth in less privileged communities are further engaged in performing arts and; 
c) Capacities of performing arts are strengthened, diversified and promoted at various levels.
